userdoc.notice: This contract generates and controls circulation of NRGTokens for facilitating energy trading. It also simulates an energy market where users can register, prosumers can inject energy and supply energy, consumers can demand energy, and the energy market can match the prosumers and consumers based on their energy s_demands and s_supplies.
